Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 面包圈！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.15,0:23:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你买了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,还有点热呢 是刚炸好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.60,0:23:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,面包圈 我想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.83,0:23:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真想趁热吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.94,0:23:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但吃过以后就吃不下晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.60,0:23:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,日向还没回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.19,0:23:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好晚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是啥 我能吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.03,0:23:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗 可以吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,手好长！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,日向正好回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.59,0:23:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.84,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.80,0:24:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.14,0:24:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是日向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.64,0:24:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.52,0:24:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,小零 姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.17,0:24:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,日向？
